snippet.title: Long Play:  The Attack of the Phantom Karate Devils
snippet.description:
Possibly the first martial arts game on a home computer.  As far as I can tell, I "won".

It looks awful but that final screen is exactly how it's supposed to look according to the developer.

Links:
